{
  "stem": "7624.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once in a while, we heard from the people who came in a small boat and told us what's going on in the newspaper and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But basically, what the Joint did or-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they're negotiating with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just can tell you what I found out after the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at the time, it was just commotion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Commotion and worry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we hear that the government wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted a certain amount of money to have us to come in there, which we didn't have no money at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So after 7 days, the captain got orders from the government to move out from the Cuban harbor, because he had to pay too much money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It needs a certain amount of money you had to pay for it, and the [INAUDIBLE] didn't want to pay no more.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, don't worry, we will cruise around the Caribbean, and we find a place for you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, the rumor started to go around that they might let us in the Island of Pines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we send our telegrams all over the world, to Panama, Argentina, the Dominican Republic, to the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We sent a telegram to Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roosevelt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't get no answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sent a telegram to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Roosevelt to let only the children in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, we didn't get no answer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were very disappointed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally, the, the happiness to leave Germany got to be depressing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was so depressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we know if you go back to Europe what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I may have mentioned something, which I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A brother of my father in 1938 made a remark against Hitler somehow.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
